cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.EC, cs.DS 

The paper deals with the problem of estimating the incentive compatibility of various mechanisms, which is a central topic in game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). The paper also uses techniques from machine learning and optimization, which suggests that it could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with optimization problems, which could place it under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.EC (Economics and Computation).
